The Quimos will be a cocktail or a mix  of  many different kind of the strongest known chemos, because they weren't sure of how to treat this kind of malignes they do not know much about it, just that it was very aggressive and rare. I was sure that this treatment,  could  kill an elephant. So I  decided to put my faith in God and in His Health Message and was treated with the most kindness, dedication and love, by Dr. Luis Baez, God and Him changed my life thru a new life style! Know days, I'm living a very happy  and healthy life,  I'm  studying Naturopathy and I'm about to graduate at the end of the this year! Thank you Dr. Baez you're the best!  May our Sweet Lord Bless you always!
